title: Ocean Minded™ Back To Our Roots Collection
description: The Ocean Minded™ Back To Our Roots Collection is just that, a renewed focus on the core styles that maintain the heritage of our brand. For 2014 we take our iconic styles and update them using luxe trends, ornamentation, texture, new materials and color freshness. We also update classic silhouettes, look back into our archives and reintroduce original styles that bring the past into the future.
